  "metaTitle": "P-Value Calculator — Z, T & Chi-Square Tests",
  "metaDescription": "Calculate p-values from z-scores, t-statistics, or chi-square values. Supports one-tailed and two-tailed tests. Instant significance testing. Free online tool.",
  "inputs": [
